cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper proposes a deep learning method for trajectory prediction in real time robotic systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the proposed method involves learning from data and making predictions based on visual information. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of stochastic gradient variational Bayes, which is a popular method in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method in a robotic task with hard real time constraints, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
